WEBVTT

00:00:27.917 --> 00:00:30.143
Let me tell you,

00:00:30.167 --> 00:00:33.934
my best app is my grandmother.

00:00:33.958 --> 00:00:35.875
(Laughter)

00:00:37.417 --> 00:00:39.184
She's called Mamadda.

00:00:39.208 --> 00:00:43.309
She can tell you not only today's weather

00:00:43.333 --> 00:00:46.309
but she can predict the next 12 months,

00:00:46.333 --> 00:00:51.184
if it's going to be
a good rain season or not.

00:00:51.208 --> 00:00:55.059
She can tell you just
by observing her environment,

00:00:55.083 --> 00:00:57.851
by observing the wind direction,

00:00:57.875 --> 00:00:59.559
the cloud position,

00:00:59.583 --> 00:01:01.476
the bird migration,